	* libgda/: introduced GdaColumnIndex to hold
	index properties on column level.

	* doc/C: added GdaColumnIndex to 
	documentation.

2005-01-31  Bas Driessen <bas.driessen@xobas.com>

	* providers/mysql/gda-mysql-provider.c: added functions
