	* providers/postgres/gda-postgres-provider.c: fix a crash when a table
	has no indexes for SCHEMA_FIELDS. Corrected defined size data for
	SCHEMA_FIELDS.
	* providers/postgres/utils.c: removed some TODO/FIXME lines.

